          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1716459394420-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>stock </strong>and your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 6-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1716459405348-x200.jpg",
