          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and slice lengthways finely – this is your <strong>julienne chilli</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1716459429536-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1716459429536-x400.jpg",
