            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the <strong>spinach</strong> and<strong> </strong>your <strong>clotted cream </strong>(save a generous drizzle for a garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for a final 1 min or until the spinach was wilted – this is your <strong>ruby chicken curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1716459445622-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
