            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>ruby chicken curry </strong>and top with the <strong>julienne chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
